'''Atrium Cinemas''' is a [[movie theater]] and first Digital 3D Multi-Screen Cinema Complex in [[Pakistan]] inside Atrium Mall [[Karachi]].<ref>{{cite news|title=Big screen, big plans: Atrium owners plan new complex in Sofitel Towers|url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/213337/big-screen-big-plans-atrium-owners-plan-new-complex-in-sofitel-towers/|accessdate=March 9, 2013|newspaper=[[tribune.com.pk]]|date=July 20, 2011}}</ref> Cinema was opened on December 31, 2010.<ref>{{cite web|title=About the Atrium Cinemas|url=http://cinematreasures.org/theaters/36996|publisher=cinematreasures.org|accessdate=March 9, 2013}}</ref>
